{"tid":1305822,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"建議加入時事「分類頁」功能","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:22:54.000Z","uid":37559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea12d73b8da08e9d599dfd66f36f93f5f904120f","tid":1305822,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"見到好多人成日都話同一件事發生（例如連儂牆義士被打...）會出現好多個不同既post<br />\n壞處：分散大家注意<br />\n同埋突發事件一時間會有多個post 令某啲重要行動post沉底<br />\n<br />\n我建議加入類似hashtag既功能 同一件事用同一個hashtag e.g. #光復上水 #九龍灣連儂牆<br />\n然後有一個分類頁集所有一樣hashtag既post一齊 喺熱門就只顯示分類名稱 e.g. 「光復上水」 裡面有光復上水既熱門post<br />\n同埋當日出有關既post就用hashtag 然後列入呢個分類頁裡面 方便大家獲得特定話題既資訊<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思可能講到好1999 但我既意思係類似email裡面既唔同categories咁<br />\n唔知道呢種功能技術上可唔可行 希望大家集思廣益 俾啲意見！"},{"pid":"ea66f0f488c9f8817ced92d9428a2d7c1bfbc196","tid":1305822,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbb473c88302c70215a771432cfc593bf7266de","tid":1305822,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"應該有用, 推"},{"pid":"cd0fd52f7a25ff0369f83d3807b87b2c43a00f7b","tid":1305822,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"94bdaae4026065d337f05433e531cf8f2c97ac77","tid":1305822,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd0fd52f7a25ff0369f83d3807b87b2c43a00f7b","tid":1305822,"uid":37559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我無野講</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}